is whether the commissioners designate the transaction for a hearing. That =
would throw the deal into administrative purgatory, potentially killing it,=
 as happened with Tegna and Standard General a few years ago. While the F.C=
=2EC. is technically an independent age=
ncy, Trump could put his thumb on the=20=
scale=E2=80=94his choice for the F.C.C.=E2=80=99s fifth commissioner,
Mark Meador, awaits Senate confirmation=E2=80=94and the Ellison family coul=
d marshal its political clout to push the deal through.
